{
  "text": "Re log e are not labelled, because their major parts overlap. Figure 16 : Schematic graphs of Γ [CITATION_1] , Γ [CITATION_2] and Γ [CITATION_3] , in the proof of part 5 of Proposition 1.3. Γ are not labelled, because their major parts overlap. Figure 17 : Schematic graphs of Γ [CITATION_4] , Γ [CITATION_5] and Γ [CITATION_6] , in the proof of part 6 of Proposition 1.3. Γ At last we apply the saddle point analysis, and find that the critical point ζ + yields the result e θ 1 (ζ)−τ z O(z −1/4 ), and the critical point ζ − yields the result e −θ 1 (ζ)−τ z O(z −1/4 ), and prove the results. The detailed computation is omitted.",
